# Agent Instructions

## This project uses platform-builder

Before doing ANY work on this project, load the platform-builder skill. This ensures you follow the project's phase flow, standards, and enforcement gates.

## State tracking

Read `docs/SESSION.md` first to know what phase we're in and what's active.

## Standards

All `standards/*-STANDARDS.md` files apply. The pre-commit hook runs `scripts/check-standards.sh` on every commit. If it fails, the commit is blocked.

## Key rules

- One ticket per session
- TDD (tests first)
- Update `docs/SESSION.md` after every session
- Run `scripts/check-standards.sh` before committing
- Never skip the pre-commit checklist
- Run a quality sweep per ticket: check-standards.sh + code smells + deepening opportunities + tech debt
